fields.description: Maximum share of carrier demand met from a set of technologies across a set of locations, on average over the entire model period.

fields.description: Share of carrier production met from a set of technologies across a set of locations, on average over the entire model period.

fields.name: net_import_share_min
fields.description: Minimum share of demand met from transmission technologies into a set of locations, on average over the entire model period. All transmission technologies of the chosen carrier are added automatically and technologies must thus not be defined explicitly.

fields.name: net_import_share_max
fields.description: Maximum share of demand met from transmission technologies into a set of locations, on average over the entire model period. All transmission technologies of the chosen carrier are added automatically and technologies must thus not be defined explicitly.

fields.name: net_import_share_equals
fields.description: Share of demand met from transmission technologies into a set of locations, on average over the entire model. All transmission technologies of the chosen carrier are added automatically and technologies must thus not be defined explicitly. period.

fields.name: flow_prod_min
fields.description: Minimum absolute sum of supplied energy (flow_prod) over all timesteps for a set of technologies across a set of locations.

fields.name: flow_prod_max
fields.description: Maximum absolute sum of supplied energy (flow_prod) over all timesteps for a set of technologies across a set of locations.

fields.name: flow_prod_equals
fields.description: Exact absolute sum of supplied energy (flow_prod) over all timesteps for a set of technologies across a set of locations.

fields.name: flow_con_min
fields.description: Minimum sum of consumed energy (flow_con) over all timesteps for a set of conversion/demand technologies across a set of locations. Values are negative and are relative to zero, i.e. a minimum value of -1 means that consumed energy must be < -1

fields.name: flow_con_max
fields.description: Maximum sum of consumed energy (flow_con) over all timesteps for a set of conversion/demand technologies across a set of locations. Values are negative and are relative to zero, i.e. a maximum value of -1 means that consumed energy must be > -1

fields.name: flow_con_equals
fields.description: Exact sum of consumed energy (flow_con) over all timesteps for a set of conversion/demand technologies across a set of locations. Values are negative.

fields.name: cost_max

fields.name: cost_equals
